author: Jesse J. Holland, Associated Press
title: Million Man March anniversary inspires memories
text: Photo: Doug Mills, AP FILE - In this Monday, Oct. 16, 1995 file photo, participants in the Million Man March raise their fists on the Mall in Washington. FILE - In this Monday, Oct. 16, 1995 file photo, participants in... WASHINGTON (AP) — The Million Man March is remembered by many who were there as a watershed event, despite the fact that its impact on the way America regards African-American men remains an open question 20 years later.
